{"tid":2488501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【得罪講句】睇完一輪廢票／不投票既討論之後，仲打算投廢票果班將來都會繼續俾泛民當傻閪咁舞，「活在幻想中」！！！！","createTime":"2021-04-14T09:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T10:55:21.000Z","uid":88743,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3df39d7530247c462a875b80e8c596738fc38e","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"violet\"><strong>先講結論：<br />\n香港既意識形態越繼續關注選舉，政權既維穩就變得更容易。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n「選舉」呢樣野本身個設計就係用黎避免紛爭<br />\n而「選舉」呢樣野本身係無呢個功能<br />\n要達到呢個功能<br />\n最大既先決條件就係要<span class=\"red\"><strong>夠多人「投入／參與」</strong></span>呢場選舉，in any form<br />\n要<strong><span class=\"red\">大多數人對呢場選舉有期望</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n睇返格黎個PO<br />\n其實點解要去投白票啫？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2488295\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2488295</a><br />\n<br />\n又講到白票數目多於保皇狗得票數，又可以點點點打J點樣「階段性勝利」<br />\n又話咁樣可以變成核彈，令到外國可以開放左更多救生艇方案比香港人<br />\n又用「咁唔通咩都唔做咩」呢啲邏輯<br />\n<br />\n最抵死係又講「梁頌恆已經出聲叫人投廢票」<br />\n又玩大台<br />\n呀屌你老母唔撚記得之前solomon yue點樣玩大台？<br />\n又話之前發起開臨時政府果班係鬼<br />\n又叫香港人參選？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZP3qShvRvhaHfE7feHgrFUonvThT3XHYqj2fWE9UKkkb?filename=BoWLjup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoWLjup.jpg&h=98fa33f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">根本白票／廢票／唔投票，都唔係重點<br />\n個重點係之後啲輿論點解讀咋</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>如果蘋果呀國際新聞呀KOL國際線呀真係幫香港<br />\n每個人唔投票，呢班人自然都可以帶輿論<br />\n帶到唔投票，就係香港人既表態<br />\n咁樣又可以係「一粒核彈」啦</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">除非呢班人目的都係想香港人參與選舉幫政權維穩啫</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根本你果票廢票係架垃圾黎咋<br />\n仲係度諗到咁撚神聖可以代表到啲乜有啲咩意義係度打飛機<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">「活在幻想中」<br />\n咁撚積極參與選舉<br />\n我代政府維穩部多謝你呀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日如常生活唔得？<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">有人開PO話當日搞個黃圈感謝祭，以爆買排隊作表態，我非常支持</span></strong><br />\n19/12攪黃店感謝日, 唔得閒去投票, 無人犯法  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2487027  \" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2487027  </a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">呢場選舉以WFC既心態去面對就OK<br />\n你鐘意既去投下廢票都無乜所謂<br />\n但如果你以「又變成一粒核彈」「階段性勝利」既心態去參與<br />\n你將會繼續俾泛民撚狗咁撚</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想慣，其實仲有方法反抗！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2393573\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2393573</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPqgDeuiXeWLPq9Fm6qABdXPTWsBu6XmYCUd4y9eejdie?filename=Zt7dNH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZt7dNH4.jpg&h=becd4276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地作者哈維爾叫你係極權下要<strong><span class=\"red\">「活在真實中」<br />\n<br />\n「又變成一粒核彈」「階段性勝利」「開放救生艇」等等<br />\n全部係我眼中都係「活在幻想中」<br />\n仲對呢場選舉有期望？醒未？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"21ca81711a27cd7238a6214165b06d0f4dbcaedd","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"我對兩邊冇意見<br />\n唯一覺得係要多人做<br />\n一邊一半唔湯唔水盞柒<br />\n<br />\n到時風向邊一邊我就做邊樣"},{"pid":"628ee9479fbc0055468093b128e4fe57813d144d","tid":2488501,"uid":59037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"你覺得投票率低定係白票多過當選票比較震撼？"},{"pid":"30f2c7869596a9195ba87971d35b5ab81eef48e5","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"21ca81711a27cd7238a6214165b06d0f4dbcaedd","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"我對兩邊冇意見<br />\n唯一覺得係要多人做<br />\n一邊一半唔湯唔水盞柒<br />\n<br />\n到時風向邊一邊我就做邊樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n<br />\n你覺得要「多人做」<br />\n少人做會「唔湯唔水」<br />\n<br />\n咪就係對個投票結果有期望<br />\n<br />\n我對投票結果一啲期望都無<br />\n我只係想多啲人變得醒少少<br />\n唔好再對個選舉有期望<br />\n之後再俾泛民同國際線用你對選舉既期望撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"a40703e3dcd442d0b9d302ef5f3ce22fe7408307","tid":2488501,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"我既期望就係想落中共面到時邊一邊多人反對就做邊樣"},{"pid":"76f9ea8e8c73299b959483b2d8dcc8b31aefd3ec","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30f2c7869596a9195ba87971d35b5ab81eef48e5","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"21ca81711a27cd7238a6214165b06d0f4dbcaedd","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"我對兩邊冇意見<br />\n唯一覺得係要多人做<br />\n一邊一半唔湯唔水盞柒<br />\n<br />\n到時風向邊一邊我就做邊樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n<br />\n你覺得要「多人做」<br />\n少人做會「唔湯唔水」<br />\n<br />\n咪就係對個投票結果有期望<br />\n<br />\n我對投票結果一啲期望都無<br />\n我只係想多啲人變得醒少少<br />\n唔好再對個選舉有期望<br />\n之後再俾泛民同國際線用你對選舉既期望撚狗咁撚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得又唔使過度/過輕解讀個選擇<br />\n選咩都冇意思係事實<br />\n多人做同一樣野係一種表態都係事實<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s all 冇其他implication"},{"pid":"0f4e7fb0b7fbc87a5e1415a59a8dd50aae9f955f","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"628ee9479fbc0055468093b128e4fe57813d144d","tid":2488501,"uid":59037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"你覺得投票率低定係白票多過當選票比較震撼？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"震唔震撼唔係由白票定廢票數量或投票率而定<br />\n係由事後既輿論導向而定<br />\n<br />\n你期望緊選舉事後社會既輿論反應<br />\n咪就係你對呢個選舉仲有好大既期望<br />\n<br />\n係我眼中你都係投入緊呢場選舉"},{"pid":"7ac4181ce3f10d1150bf491c2508a7d4328cea5f","tid":2488501,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"樓主有時講嘢搶口d但其實不無道理"},{"pid":"2592ba013eb856faa27bd292bf3c8a6049b4260b","tid":2488501,"uid":189799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"628ee9479fbc0055468093b128e4fe57813d144d","tid":2488501,"uid":59037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"你覺得投票率低定係白票多過當選票比較震撼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"一定係後者震撼，但前者容易做到好多。"},{"pid":"de1e465be1229220470b1f234723e13d5c9aae6a","tid":2488501,"uid":189799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76f9ea8e8c73299b959483b2d8dcc8b31aefd3ec","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30f2c7869596a9195ba87971d35b5ab81eef48e5","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"21ca81711a27cd7238a6214165b06d0f4dbcaedd","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"我對兩邊冇意見<br />\n唯一覺得係要多人做<br />\n一邊一半唔湯唔水盞柒<br />\n<br />\n到時風向邊一邊我就做邊樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n<br />\n你覺得要「多人做」<br />\n少人做會「唔湯唔水」<br />\n<br />\n咪就係對個投票結果有期望<br />\n<br />\n我對投票結果一啲期望都無<br />\n我只係想多啲人變得醒少少<br />\n唔好再對個選舉有期望<br />\n之後再俾泛民同國際線用你對選舉既期望撚狗咁撚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得又唔使過度/過輕解讀個選擇<br />\n選咩都冇意思係事實<br />\n多人做同一樣野係一種表態都係事實<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s all 冇其他implication"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"我都同意，個選舉玩法任佢定，其實點都輸，宜家只係諗下有咩方法輸少啲"},{"pid":"4fc5bf02e936c2f718332d65dafbce8caefba4d3","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76f9ea8e8c73299b959483b2d8dcc8b31aefd3ec","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30f2c7869596a9195ba87971d35b5ab81eef48e5","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"21ca81711a27cd7238a6214165b06d0f4dbcaedd","tid":2488501,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"我對兩邊冇意見<br />\n唯一覺得係要多人做<br />\n一邊一半唔湯唔水盞柒<br />\n<br />\n到時風向邊一邊我就做邊樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n<br />\n你覺得要「多人做」<br />\n少人做會「唔湯唔水」<br />\n<br />\n咪就係對個投票結果有期望<br />\n<br />\n我對投票結果一啲期望都無<br />\n我只係想多啲人變得醒少少<br />\n唔好再對個選舉有期望<br />\n之後再俾泛民同國際線用你對選舉既期望撚狗咁撚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得又唔使過度/過輕解讀個選擇<br />\n選咩都冇意思係事實<br />\n多人做同一樣野係一種表態都係事實<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s all 冇其他implication"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:44:04.000Z","msg":"無乜所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbd63e821f214de110d6f0475f4629ae293dcd8","tid":2488501,"uid":189799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f4e7fb0b7fbc87a5e1415a59a8dd50aae9f955f","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"628ee9479fbc0055468093b128e4fe57813d144d","tid":2488501,"uid":59037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"你覺得投票率低定係白票多過當選票比較震撼？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"震唔震撼唔係由白票定廢票數量或投票率而定<br />\n係由事後既輿論導向而定<br />\n<br />\n你期望緊選舉事後社會既輿論反應<br />\n咪就係你對呢個選舉仲有好大既期望<br />\n<br />\n係我眼中你都係投入緊呢場選舉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"咁你開post討論都係投入選舉啦"},{"pid":"984bd5f3f588efdf09a6d4583e48525064bcc263","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你覺得投票率低定係白票多過當選票比較震撼？</blockquote>震唔震撼唔係由白票定廢票數量或投票率而定<br />\n係由事後既輿論導向而定<br />\n<br />\n你期望緊選舉事後社會既輿論反應<br />\n咪就係你對呢個選舉仲有好大既期望<br />\n<br />\n係我眼中你都係投入緊呢場選舉</blockquote>咁你開post討論都係投入選舉啦</blockquote><br />\n勁撚多人拉PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係咪又可以講：我開呢個PO又做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我開PO討論唔係期望選舉結果<br />\n係期望要班人要改變個mantality呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我下面第二個結論咪講左<br />\n如果你唔係以「又變成一粒核彈」「階段性勝利」既心態去投票<br />\n你投白票廢票唔投票都無所謂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde7ee3bcdfa733b5cf2a0e29d7131a7d48d86fe","tid":2488501,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"628ee9479fbc0055468093b128e4fe57813d144d","tid":2488501,"uid":59037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"你覺得投票率低定係白票多過當選票比較震撼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"白兵支持者黎你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然而家個個話投白票， 梗係屌人投白票=參加選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再顯出自己有幾高智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己諗清楚 無論白票又好，唔投票又好，基本上白兵都係企係不敗之地咁尻up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeab2c330cc42082bca0bef19452d2fd2c688de","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7ac4181ce3f10d1150bf491c2508a7d4328cea5f","tid":2488501,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"樓主有時講嘢搶口d但其實不無道理"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"多謝棒場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過陣間又會俾人起底話我五毛分化撚<br />\n之後就會話「五毛講既野，做相反就對了」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804d5349cdf183b7b8b0cd55bbbacf27816abfda","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a40703e3dcd442d0b9d302ef5f3ce22fe7408307","tid":2488501,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"我既期望就係想落中共面到時邊一邊多人反對就做邊樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"到時泛民可能叫你唔好浪費果一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1411b1171819768ea7c3e400b3917b0987a03d52","tid":2488501,"uid":277816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbeab2c330cc42082bca0bef19452d2fd2c688de","tid":2488501,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7ac4181ce3f10d1150bf491c2508a7d4328cea5f","tid":2488501,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"樓主有時講嘢搶口d但其實不無道理"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"多謝棒場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過陣間又會俾人起底話我五毛分化撚<br />\n之後就會話「五毛講既野，做相反就對了」<img src=